al/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n荷里活 矽谷 華爾街 大學 個個都想發大財賺easy money 賺人民幣 <br />\n共產黨利用返資本主義去收買返美國政商界轉頭<br />\n共產黨應該更加估唔到既係班白皮豬原來係咁易對付<br />\n俾錢就可以搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當年克林頓說服國會將美中貿易同人權問題脫勾<br />\n共產黨應該都係咁搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T23:30:09.000Z","msg":"冇錯 真係好廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c61d2e7ed4abd9d2e005f26ab4b97f36fe9d3f29","tid":2242180,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T23:34:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128f7837e9c6b413f8637df410eedf201cd2df71","tid":2242180,"uid":204533,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"730177f82e070358125bcd814ec66ac60dab797c","tid":2242180,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T23:28:56.000Z","msg":"有冇英文新聞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T23:34:47.000Z","msg":"US Secretary of State Mike Pompeo on Tuesday asked Washington's think tanks to disclose foreign funding, warning of Chinese and Russian backing for the institutions known for wide influence on US policy.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.france24.com/en/20201013-pompeo-asks-us-think-tanks-to-disclose-foreign-funding\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.france24.com%2Fen%2F20201013-pompeo-asks-us-think-tanks-to-disclose-foreign-funding&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2gZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=259cb21f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.france24.com/en/20201013-pompeo-asks-us-think-tanks-to-disclose-foreign-funding</a><br />\n<br />\nThe Trump administration is demanding that U.S. think tanks and academic institutions publicly disclose what funding they receive from foreign governments or otherwise risk losing access to State Department officials.<br />\n<br />\nThe move, unveiled in a statement Tuesday by Secretary of State Mike Pompeo, comes amid growing bipartisan concern about the role outside governments, ranging from China to the United Arab Emirates, play in shaping academic and policy debates in the United States.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;To protect the integrity of civil society institutions, the [State] Department requests henceforth that think tanks and other foreign policy organizations that wish to engage with the department disclose prominently on their websites funding they receive from foreign governments, including state-owned or state-operated subsidiary entities,&rdquo; Pompeo said in the statement.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.politico.com/news/2020/10/13/trump-think-tanks-foreign-funding-429209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2020%2F10%2F13%2Ftrump-think-tanks-foreign-funding-429209&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2gZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=a13f784c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.politico.com/news/2020/10/13/trump-think-tanks-foreign-funding-429209</a>"},{"pid":"196b4764dc5b3ca9e015e6ebea6ea6e481d73864","tid":2242180,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T23:36:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b2c8ef135780c02e98f7967b115f61997c487b","tid":2242180,"uid":245713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"daff087ca00e530030c68aa0d48998ecc8334613","tid":2242180,"uid":204533,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T23:13:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就在蓬佩奧發表聲明之前，&ldquo;透明國際&rdquo;發布了《 2020年出口腐敗報告》。<br />\n<br />\n這份報告指出，<strong>外國官員的賄賂給世界各國造成了巨大的損失和後果，這種情況在病毒大流行發生後變得更加嚴重。</strong><br />\n<br />\n報告說，在經合組織條約簽署以來的20多年中，大多數國家在履行自己的反腐義務方面做得還很不夠。事實上，大部分國家在積極執法方面與該組織2018年發布上次報告時相比出現了顯著的倒退。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">報告指出，中國、香港和印度在打擊國外腐敗現象和洗錢方面無所作為。新加坡在這方面採取的舉措非常有限。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n報告在談到中國情況的時候表示，最近幾年，中國在相關立法方面取得了一些進展，但與強有力的國內反腐執法相比，針對國外發生的腐敗現像似乎沒有得到重視。</blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T23:38:21.000Z","msg":"corruptiin destory the world"},{"pid":"6a4e1cdb48a2241065c273ff41dd1ac478d28fd5","tid":2242180,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T23:40:32.000Z","msg":"老董？"},{"pid":"ae9724c1e920033911ee93a861ef770180007fce","tid":2242180,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T23:41:28.000Z","msg":"同聯合國一樣，又係用銀彈買票上拉"},{"pid":"9cda34f34574dca5d2ecd65d171d6e2abe7642c6","tid":2242180,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T23:41:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253d64facd75c207f3fffd4f0a5f7762f41dd093","tid":2242180,"uid":282569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T23:45:55.000Z","msg":"咁先係路㗎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁先可以滅絕d暗共左膠 同大巴大巴咁摑班on9左膠"},{"pid":"3ad8a5f42f221cfba537feeb926a09432fef17c0","tid":2242180,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T00:00:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c41c661d8eaadd930d61f069494ee34dfe8050","tid":2242180,"uid":168818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T00:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e9efa434f351c3a06f6592711501da79d528f49","tid":2242180,"uid":13745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d9b1dd2b6e16e7b12356f77b2f2b811d72a4ee5a","tid":2242180,"uid":91397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aa47b92da3b04a4bfbae405969e4a1bb372263eb","tid":2242180,"uid":13745,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T23:24:03.000Z","msg":"一早就應該要做啦<br />\n而家先做<im